<body>
    <h1>Lasagna</h1>
    <img src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/gfhfsBPt46s/maxresdefault.jpg" alt="">
    <h4>A very simple ricipe that involves tomato sauce, cheese, meat, spices and strips of pasta.</h4>
    <br>
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Ground beef</li>
        <li>Garlic gloves</li>
        <li>salt</li>
        <li>tomato sauce</li>
        <li>ricotta cheese</li>
        <li>mozzerella cheese</li>
        <li>lasagna noodles</li>
    </ul>
    <br>
    <h2>Directions</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Take ground beef and mix with salt tomato sauce and stirr it well</li>
        <li>cover and simmer 1 hour</li>
        <li>cook lasagna noodles</li>
        <li>spray baking pan with cooking spray</li>
        <li>mix mozzerella and ricotta cheese together</li>
        <li>layer the meat, cheese and lasagna noodles evenly on the pan</li>
        <li>bake at 375F for 40-60mins or until the cheese has melted</li>
    </ol>
